data.name: label28.Text
data.value: Following our underwriting guidelines, PRMD will evaluate the application submitted and determine the correct classification (specialty), calculating premium based on actual procedures performed by the prospect insured.

data.name: label46.Text
data.value: Tariff quoted includes a surcharge of 0.9% determined by the Commissioner of Insurance of Puerto Rico for the purpose of recovering the unreimbursed assessments paid by Puerto Rico Medical Defense Insurance Company to the Puerto Rico Property and Casualty Insurance Guaranty Association. As required by the Commissioner of Insurance of Puerto Rico, once the policy is issued the surcharge will be segregated from the premium.
